org.jamsim.ascape.stats

Class CollectorFunction<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ascape.util.data.StatCollector
      • org.ascape.util.data.StatCollectorCSA
        • org.ascape.util.data.StatCollectorCondCSA
          • org.jamsim.ascape.stats.CollectorFunction<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the scape member this collector gets data from.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable, Conditional, DataPoint, HasName
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CollectorFunctionPerIteration

    public class CollectorFunction<T>
extends StatCollectorCondCSA
    Collect data values on a subset of the scape. The subset to collect is defined by a function predicate. The value to collect is defined by a value function.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
    Oliver Mannion
